<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Break Started - WorkHole</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7 0%, #a29bfe 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .break-info { background-color: #e8f4fd; border-left: 4px solid #6c5ce7; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { background-color: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>☕ Break Started!</h1>
            <p>Time to recharge and refresh</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= employee.firstName %>!</h2>
            
            <p>Your break has started successfully. Enjoy your time! 😊</p>
            
            <div class="break-info">
                <h3>📋 Break Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Type:</strong> <%= breakType %></p>
                <p><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= duration %> minutes</p>
                <p><strong>Started at:</strong> <%= startTime.toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: true }) %></p>
                <p><strong>Expected end:</strong> <%= new Date(startTime.getTime() + duration * 60000).toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: true }) %></p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>💡 Make the most of your break:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Stay hydrated 💧</li>
                <li>Stretch your body 🤸‍♂️</li>
                <li>Take deep breaths 🌬️</li>
                <li>Relax your mind 🧘‍♀️</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Remember to return on time to stay productive! ⏰</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>WorkHole - Employee Management System</p>
            <p>Taking care of your well-being! 💜</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>